sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Node as ESP32 Node
  participant Broker as MQTT Broker
  participant Mqtt as mqttService
  participant ReadSvc as ReadingService
  participant PollRepo as PolluantRepository
  participant AlertRepo as AlertRepository
  participant ReadDB as readings
  participant AlertDB as alerts
  participant API as REST APIs
  participant UI as Frontend Dashboard

  Node->>Broker: publish emissions/zone/pollutant {value, unit, sensorType}
  Broker->>Mqtt: deliver message
  Mqtt->>ReadSvc: ingestReading(sensorId, polluantId, value...)
  ReadSvc->>PollRepo: findById(polluantId)
  PollRepo-->>ReadSvc: regulatoryLimit + warningThreshold
  ReadSvc->>ReadDB: create reading (isValid)

  alt value <= warningThreshold
    ReadSvc->>AlertRepo: autoResolve(open alert)
    AlertRepo->>AlertDB: set resolvedAt
  else value > warningThreshold
    ReadSvc->>AlertRepo: create or update active alert
    AlertRepo->>AlertDB: save severity + message
  end

  API->>ReadDB: GET /api/readings/latest
  API->>AlertDB: GET /api/alerts
  API-->>UI: concentrations + alert status + comparaison normes

  Note over UI: Affichage couleur selon ecart a la norme\n(Warning / High / Critical)